<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَلَرُبَّمَا نَالَ الأَبِيُّ الْحُرُّ مِنْ طَاغُوتِهِ لَقَبَ السَّجِينْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَالْمَنُّ كُلُّ الْمَنِّ مِنْ ذَاكَ الْكَرِيمْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَنْعِمْ بِهَذَا الْحِلْمِ مِنْ ذَاكَ الْحَلِيمْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>يَرْضَى بِحُرٍّ فِي الْحَيَاةْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَعَلِمْتَ كَيْفَ الآنَ صَارَ النِّفْطُ أَغْلَى مِنْ دَمِكْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فِي أَرْضِ قَوْمِكَ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>بَيْنَ أَهْلِكَ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>هَلْ تَرَى<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>لا شَيءَ أَرْخَصُ مِنْ دَمِكْ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَتُرِيدُ مِنْ أَعْدَاءِ دِينِكَ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>أَنْ يَحِنُّوا أَوْ تَرِقَّ قُلُوبُهُمْ لِدِمَائِكْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>هَذَا جُنُونْ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>طَاغُوتُكُمْ فِي بَاسِهِ مَعَهُمْ يَهُونُ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>